#MEM id=prompt-qa source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/atlas/skills/custom/prompt-qa/SKILL.md savings=11%
M||tx|---
M||name|pm-qa
M||desc|yv-specific pre-handoff pm checklist. Run on every pm before it reaches px. Catches contradictory style tags, vt forbidden elements, missing Avoid list items, and platform dimension gaps. Reduces px's QC rejection rate.
M||vers|1.0.0
M||tx|---
M|Purp|tx|A pm w/ contradictory tags produces inconsistent batches. A pm missing the Avoid list produces images that technically pass the style spec but violate the br. This skill catches both — at the individual pm level, not the cg level. The triple-pass reviews overall direction qual; this skill checks the actual string px will use.
M|Purp|tx|---
M|Chec|Scan|
M|Chec|tx|\| Tag A \| Incompatible w/ \| Why \|
M|Chec|tx|\|-------\|------------------\|-----\|
M|Chec|tx|\| `candid` \| `studio-lit` \| Candid = unposed/natural; studio-lit = controlled setup \|
M|Chec|tx|\| `editorial` \| `catalogue` \| Editorial = conceptual; catalogue = commercial pd focus \|
M|Chec|tx|\| `editorial` \| `pd shot` \| Same conflict as above \|
M|Chec|tx|\| `raw` \| `polished` \| Contradictory finish \|
M|Chec|tx|\| `minimal` \| `maximalist` \| Opposite compositional philosophies \|
M|Chec|tx|\| `natural light` \| `neon` \| Conflicting light sources \|
M|Chec|tx|\| `natural light` \| `studio flash` \| Conflicting light sources \|
M|Chec|tx|\| `lifestyle` \| `pd shot` \| Different compositional register \|
M|Chec|tx|\| `moody` \| `bright and airy` \| Contradictory mood \|
M|Chec|tx|\| `documentary` \| `staged` \| Contradictory authenticity signals \|
M|Chec|tx|\| `bokeh` \| `tack sharp everything` \| Contradictory depth of field \|
M|Chec|tx|\| `close-up portrait` \| `wide establishing shot` \| Contradictory composition \|
M|Chec|**Ru|** If a contradiction is found, resolve it — don't send both tags hoping the md will figure it out.
M|Chec|tx|---
M|Chec|**No|**
M|Chec|it|Busy patterns or busy backgrounds
M|Chec|- St|perfect poses, fake smiles, overly generic settings
M|Chec|- Pr|sale banners, price text, "Buy Now" text within the im
M|Chec|it|Harsh flash or hi-key flat lighting
M|Chec|it|Catalogue-style white-background pd shots (unless pd-only cg is specifically approved)
M|Chec|it|Any element that reads as fast fashion or disposable
M|Chec|**Ho|**
M|Chec|- Mo|coins, cash, piggy banks, dollar signs, stacks of notes
M|Chec|it|Dark or dramatic backgrounds (unless explicitly br-approved for that cg)
M|Chec|- Ge|suits in boardrooms, handshakes, stock-photo professionals
M|Chec|- Cl|upward graph lines, padlocks, checkmarks in shields
M|Chec|it|Overly clinical/sterile environments
M|Chec|it|Generic phone mockups that cld belong to any SaaS br
M|Chec|fix|** If any forbidden element is present in the pm or is likely to appear based on the style tags — add it to the Avoid list explicitly.
M|Chec|tx|---
M|Chec|Ever|
M|Chec|tx|\| Requirement \| Standard \|
M|Chec|tx|\|------------\|---------\|
M|Chec|tx|\| Minimum items \| 3 specific items \|
M|Chec|tx|\| Specificity \| Each item names something concrete — not "avoid bad qual" \|
M|Chec|tx|\| vt-specific \| At least 1 item is specific to the vt's known fl patterns \|
M|Chec|tx|\| cg-specific \| At least 1 item is specific to this cg's risk (what cld easily go wrong here?) \|
M|Chec|**Re|** Avoid list is empty, has only generic items ("avoid blurry images"), or has fewer than 3 entries.
M|Chec|tx|---
M|Chec|Conf|
M|Chec|tx|\| Platform \| vt \| Ratio \| Dimensions \|
M|Chec|tx|\|---------\|---------\|-------\|-----------\|
M|Chec|| In|1 or 4:5 \| 1080×1080 or 1080×1350 \|
M|Chec|| In|16 \| 1080×1920 \|
M|Chec|| Ti|16 \| 1080×1920 \|
M|Chec|| Li|1 or 1.91:1 \| 1080×1080 or 1200×628 \|
M|Chec|| Yo|9 \| 1280×720 \|
M|Chec|fix|** If dimensions aren't specified, add them to the production brief before handoff. px shd not have to infer the target format.
M|Chec|tx|---
M|Ambi|Fina|"If this pm were given to three different AI md, wld they all produce images in the same aesthetic register?"
M|Ambi|it|If yes → specific enough. Proceed.
M|Ambi|it|If no → identify the ambiguous term (usually the mood or style tag) and replace w/ a more specific descriptor.
M|Ambi|**Co|**
M|Ambi|tx|\| Vague \| Replace w/ \|
M|Ambi|tx|\|-------\|-------------\|
M|Ambi|| `b|`soft, editorial, quiet confidence` \|
M|Ambi|| `p|`clean workspace, natural light, focused` \|
M|Ambi|| `m|`minimal, white space, geometric` \|
M|Ambi|| `a|`Scandinavian editorial, muted palette` \|
M|Ambi|| `l|`soft cashmere, clean neutrals, considered composition` \|
M|Ambi|tx|---
M|Outp|Afte|
M|Outp|tx|```
M|Outp|Chec|[none found / resolved: X replaced Y bc Z]
M|Outp|Chec|[none present / removed: X from pm]
M|Outp|Chec|[passed: N items / added: X]
M|Outp|Chec|[confirmed: ratio X / added to brief]
M|Outp|Ambi|[passed / resolved: X replaced w/ Y]
M|Outp|Prom|READY FOR px / REVISED — see updated pm below
M|Outp|tx|```